WEBVTT

00:00:14.020 --> 00:00:15.568
By now, I'm sure you know

00:00:15.568 --> 00:00:17.540
that in just about anything you do in life,

00:00:17.540 --> 00:00:19.246
you need numbers.

00:00:19.246 --> 00:00:20.273
In particular, though,

00:00:20.273 --> 00:00:22.502
some fields don't just need a few numbers,

00:00:22.502 --> 00:00:24.222
they need lots of them.

00:00:24.222 --> 00:00:26.248
How do you keep track of all those numbers?

00:00:26.248 --> 00:00:28.164
Well, mathematicians dating back

00:00:28.164 --> 00:00:30.129
as early as ancient China